        <mxCell id="balance_text" value="✓ INPUTS from Level-1 Process 5:&#xa;  • compiled harnesses (from Process 4)&#xa;  • harness binaries (from D5: Harness Code)&#xa;  • resource allocation (from Process 8)&#xa;&#xa;✓ OUTPUTS from Level-1 Process 5:&#xa;  • crash data (to Process 6)&#xa;  • crash artifacts (to D6: Crash Artifacts)&#xa;  • performance metrics (to Monitoring System)&#xa;  • resource requests (to Process 8)&#xa;  • metrics data (to D8: System Metrics)&#xa;&#xa;All boundary flows are preserved with identical names and connections." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
