        <mxCell id="summary_text" value="Internal Flow Sequence:&#xa;1. Initialize campaign with resources → 2. Prepare seed corpus&#xa;3. Execute fuzzer with harnesses → 4. Monitor execution in real-time&#xa;5. Detect crashes and violations → 6. Collect coverage data&#xa;7. Generate comprehensive campaign report&#xa;&#xa;Key Decision Points:&#xa;• Campaign initialization coordinates with resource manager&#xa;• Monitoring provides feedback loop to control fuzzer execution&#xa;• Parallel collection of crashes and coverage data&#xa;• Real-time metrics sent to monitoring system&#xa;• Campaign report aggregates all execution data" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
